1 paid or any prior biennium. A reimbursement may not be made to the extent funds are not available
2 in the fund to make the reimbursement.
3 (6)(a) Total actual Oregon expenses supporting a claim for reimbursement under this section
4 must be verified by the Oregon Film and Video Office. The filmmaker or local media production
5 services company must submit to the office proof of the actual Oregon expenses. The proof must
6 include any documentation that may be required by the office in its discretion to verify the actual
